Package: YLLgmethods
Title: Years of Life Lost via the G-Formula
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(
      "Shuntaro", "Sato",
      email   = "shuntaro.sato.stat@gmail.com",
      role    = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6055-3649")
    )
Description: Estimates Years of Life Lost (YLL) and counterfactual life
    expectancy under user-specified interventions on a binary exposure using
    the parametric g-formula on the attained-age time scale. Supports ATE,
    ATT, ATC, and stochastic / population interventions, with bootstrap
    confidence intervals and helpers for plotting conditional and marginal
    survival curves.
